PrecisORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (LITTLE SALMON/CARMCACKS FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which provides for (a) the withdrawal from disposal of land in the Yukon until February 1, 2008, and (b) the repeal of a similar Withdrawal from Disposal Order made in 1998.
